pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: nav-bar
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [0, 0, 1280, 50]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$navBg"

  - elementId: nav-left-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [0, 0, 4, 720]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: gradient
      gradientType: linear
      angle: 90
      stops:
        - {position: 0, color: "#432879"}
        - {position: 1, color: "#8A7BB550"}

  - elementId: nav-chapter-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [20, 0, 900, 50]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "#FFFFFFCC"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: 02 理论基础与相关工作 / 2.1 相关工作综述

  - elementId: nav-page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1200, 0, 60, 50]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "05"

  - elementId: title-accent-mark
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [12, 68, 4, 40]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: gradient
      gradientType: linear
      angle: 90
      stops:
        - {position: 0, color: "#432879"}
        - {position: 1, color: "#8A7BB5"}

  - elementId: page-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [24, 68, 1000, 40]
    content:
      style: "$pageTitle"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>相关工作综述与本文定位</strong></p>

  - elementId: title-sep
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [24, 116, 1232, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#C8BEE0"

  # Bullet 1
  - elementId: b1-mark
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [24, 136, 6, 36]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: b1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [44, 136, 1200, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>监督学习方法（2015–2020）</strong></p>

  - elementId: b1-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [44, 170, 1200, 26]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      text: |
        <p>以 ResNet、VGG 为代表的深度卷积网络取得了里程碑式突破，但高度依赖大规模标注数据，标注成本极高。</p>

  - elementId: sep1
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [24, 210, 1232, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#EEE8F4"

  # Bullet 2
  - elementId: b2-mark
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [24, 226, 6, 36]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$secondary"

  - elementId: b2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [44, 226, 1200, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>自监督预训练方法（2020–2022）</strong></p>

  - elementId: b2-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [44, 260, 1200, 26]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      text: |
        <p>BERT、SimCLR、MAE 等自监督方法缓解了标注瓶颈，但在特定垂直领域微调时仍面临域偏移问题。</p>

  - elementId: sep2
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [24, 300, 1232, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#EEE8F4"

  # Bullet 3
  - elementId: b3-mark
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [24, 316, 6, 36]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: b3-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [44, 316, 1200, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>大模型 + 提示学习（2022–至今）</strong></p>

  - elementId: b3-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [44, 350, 1200, 26]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      text: |
        <p>以 GPT-4、LLaVA 为代表的大模型涌现出强大的零样本能力，但部署成本极高且推理延迟难以满足实时需求。</p>

  - elementId: sep3
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [24, 390, 1232, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#EEE8F4"

  # Bullet 4
  - elementId: b4-mark
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [24, 406, 6, 36]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: b4-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [44, 406, 1200, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>研究空白与本文切入点</strong></p>

  - elementId: b4-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [44, 440, 1200, 26]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      text: |
        <p>如何在轻量化约束下实现跨域自适应，是当前尚未被充分解决的问题，也是本文研究的核心切入点。</p>

  # 结论强调框
  - elementId: insight-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [24, 492, 1232, 56]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$lightPurple"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$midPurple"

  - elementId: insight-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [40, 492, 1196, 56]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: true
      text: |
        <p><strong>本文定位：</strong>在现有方法基础上，提出兼顾效率与跨域适应性的轻量化方案，填补上述研究空白。</p>

  - elementId: page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1200, 680, 50, 24]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$secondary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "5"
